text: Tord Karlsson (born 4 December 1941) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kiruna Municipality
